  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>spelt</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiling water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 20 min or until tender (it will still have a slight bite when cooked)</p><p>Once cooked, drain and rinse under <strong>cold water</strong> to cool</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-chorizo-roasted-veg-and-spelt-salad/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and chop your <strong>red onion[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thick strips</p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-chorizo-roasted-veg-and-spelt-salad/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>the <strong>onion wedges </strong>and <strong>pepper strips</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!) with your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> and put the tray[s] in the oven for 12-15 min or until everything is beginning to char – this is your <strong>smoky roasted veg</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-chorizo-roasted-veg-and-spelt-salad/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> diced chorizo</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until crisp</p><p>Once crisp, drain the <strong>crispy chorizo </strong>from the <strong>chorizo oil</strong>, reserving both</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-chorizo-roasted-veg-and-spelt-salad/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Roll your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-chorizo-roasted-veg-and-spelt-salad/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and your <strong>mayo</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>reserved chorizo oil </strong>and a squeeze of <strong>lemon juice</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> and stir it all together – this is your <strong>chorizo dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-chorizo-roasted-veg-and-spelt-salad/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong> then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>salad </strong>to a bowl with the <strong>cooled spelt</strong>, <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong>, <strong>smoky roasted veg</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped parsley</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and a spoonful of the <strong>chorizo dressing</strong> and toss – this is your <strong>smoky roasted veg & spelt salad</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining</strong> <strong>lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/smoky-chorizo-roasted-veg-and-spelt-salad/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>smoky roasted veg & spelt salad</strong> topped with the <strong>crispy chorizo</strong>, <strong>remaining chopped parsley </strong>and <strong>remaining chorizo dressing</strong></p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
